<hi rend="latintype">Besenius</hi></rs>? Wenn man <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29999" subtype="implied">Heinrich</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t und dies erlebt.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <signed>H.</signed></closer><postscript><p>Viele Grüße Deiner <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs></p></postscript></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb10815">
